	  not be installed.

2004-01-04 11:48  epaepa

	* lib/XMLTV.pm.in: 'require' rather than 'use' XMLTV::Date because
	  XMLTV.pm is loaded at build time and XMLTV::Date is not available
	  then.  (Sourceforge bug #870171.)

